snippet.title: Terror Spikys - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Terror Spikys - Official Announcement Trailer





guy's brand new killer cactus game trailer is announced 



also check official trailer of this game

add your wishlist here - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2601420/Terror_Spikys/

developed by- @RefugiumGames 

link- https://youtu.be/kAfNBS_6TXc?si=TYmt0aRKnUFFv7Wn



about this game👇👇

Get hired as a Cactus Hunter, explore the killer cacti infested open-world with your truck, help villagers in return for valuables and wipe out the so-called Terror Spikys

I hope you enjoy this trailer

---------------------------------------------------------
